com.flowpowered.cerealization.config

Class ConfigurationHolderConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.flowpowered.cerealization.config.ConfigurationWrapper
      • com.flowpowered.cerealization.config.ConfigurationHolderConfiguration
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Configuration, ConfigurationNodeSource

    public abstract class ConfigurationHolderConfiguration
extends ConfigurationWrapper
    This is a configuration holder class that takes another Configuration and wraps some reflection to get all the fields in the subclass that have values of the type ConfigurationHolder. These fields will be automatically associated with the attached configuration and have their default values loaded into the configuration as needed on load
